  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is buffet style with freshly baked cakes, breads and pastries along with hot dishes, cold cuts and local cheeses.</p>
<p>Dinner is four-courses with a salad and starter buffet. The restaurant where half board is taken, is elegant with large windows overlooking the garden and the menu changes daily. The hotel request a smart dress code at dinner, with no shorts to be worn.</p>
<p>If you're after a nightcap, you can grab a cocktail or glass of wine from the bar and head out onto the terrace which overlooks the lake.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
