  <description><![CDATA[<p>It’s hard to choose our favourite thing about Hotel Bellevue San Lorenzo. It’s a close call between the infinity pool that looks out over the lake and the gardens, and the spa with a Turkish bath, sauna and sensory showers. The hotel welcomes guests aged 16 years and over only. </p>
<h2>Classic Italian Style</h2>
<p>When you arrive you'll find it hard not to be impressed. Beautiful lawns surround six classic Italian villas. The rooms are either in the villas or the main building and are light and airy. Upgrade to one with a lake view and balcony if you can. The restaurant's fantastic and serves proper Italian food including fresh fish and risotto.</p>
<h2>Walk or cycle into Malcesine</h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a> is about a 15 minute walk away and can easily be reached along the lakeside promenade. The hotel also has bikes available, so you can take the lakefront cycle lane into town or hit the road and head up into the hills for some of the best views over <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>.</p>]]></description>
