  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Mountain View Rooms</strong> sleep up to two people and have a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Side Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people and have partial views of the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people. They have a balcony or terrace with side or frontal lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 30m² and sleep two people. They have a balcony or terrace and side or frontal lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Rooms for sole use</strong> are available for a supplement. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking. Preferences cannot be guaranteed.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Mini-fridge</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General Information:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Rooms will be allocated in one of the five buildings located in the hotel grounds; styles and room sizes may vary.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A resort tax of approx. €1.50 per person per night is payable locally.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
